Quick map with climb, diffrent types of bhop, ljs from beginner to 245 & expert lj scs, ladder strafing and more.

Took me a few hours to manage to pack this bitch together due to broken textures so you may have seen a few versions allready that I trashed.

edit: let me clear up some confusion, yes it's a simple design because i wasnt even gonna make another map and i sure wasnt about to spend months on it. If you don't like it, if you think the levels are too easy or boring then don't play it :)
